window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>\"That which doesn't kill me is going to wish it had.\" </b></p> <p>Do you love hunting monsters? Dark worlds? Swords and sorcery? </p> <p>Alex is a Glitch Hunter, member of a house of monster hunters that possess mysterious bracers allowing them to see the world with the interface of a video game. Even with the edge that offers, most Glitch Hunters die young, thrown by quests into areas of deadly conflict. Alex's first quest draws him to a city with a grisly past, and unless he can discern truth from lies in time, an even darker future.</p>"; 
